public abstract class AbstractSetAcc<T extends GraphicComponent,​S extends AbstractGraphicComponentSet<T,​S>,​L extends AbstractGraphicComponentList<T,​S,​L>,​R extends Run<T,​L>,​A extends AbstractSetAcc<T,​S,​L,​R,​A>>
extends AbstractAcc<T,​S,​L,​R,​A>
implements SetListener<T>
This class provides a category of acceptance conditions of which each condition is a set of states or transitions. Büchi condition, classic condition, and co-Büchi condition belong to this category.
Author:
Ming-Hsien Tsai
